name: HikariCP
tagline: A solid high-performance JDBC connection pool at last.
body:
### World Class
HikariCP is a high-performance low-overhead JDBC connection pool for Java.

#### Support
Google discussion group [HikariCP here](https://groups.google.com/d/forum/hikari-cp)

#### Requirements
 * Oracle Java 6 and above
 * Javassist 3.18.1+ library
 * slf4j library
